creator: Covenant Church & Covenant Christian School
descriptionHtml:
Access the latest content from Covenant Church. Connect with our online community. Receive instant inspiration and encouragement — anytime, anywhere.

The Covenant Church app makes it easy to…

* Watch all the latest sermons from Covenant Church.

* Join LIVE worship experiences.

* Chat and connect with other in Covenant Church

* Discover ways to get involved at Covenant Church.


Covenant Church is a multi-site, ministry founded by Senior Pastor Ken Peters. The Moses Lake Campus is led by Pastor Seth Haberman and the Spokane Campus is led by Pastor Matt Shea. Our worship experiences are broadcasted live from both campuses every weekend.
descriptionShort: Access the latest content from Covenant Church. Give, watch, connect and receive

appDetails.recentChangesHtml: If enabled, the app will show the viewer a prompt to take an action at a designated time during a live stream.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
- We've consolidated Listen and Watch into a single Play button on the media player. Users can still switch between listening and watching modes.
- If enabled, Messaging now features an option to silence all notifications for a predetermined period of time.
- You can now start Picture-in-picture playback in the player to watch video and browse the app at the same time.
- Misc. bug fixes and improvements.
